                                        <width>166</width>
                                    </dimensions>
                                </extent>
                                <condition>A total of 12 leaves are missing at different places in
                                    between the surviving leaves. The lower part of fol 14 is torn
                                    out. Here and there smaller damages, tears etc.</condition>
                            </supportDesc>
                            <layoutDesc>
